The teak magic wardrobe can be built in the magic wardrobe space of the costume room in a player-owned house. It requires 60 Construction to upgrade the carved oak magic wardrobe and when built, it gives 360 experience. The player must have a hammer and a saw in their inventory to build it.

The teak magic wardrobe can hold 21 of the magic armour/robe sets listed below.

The player must have a [[hammer]] and a [[saw]] in their inventory to build it.

The teak magic wardrobe can hold 21 of the magic armour/robe sets listed below.
